name: Lolland
tag_list: india, humour, comedy, satire, spoof, video, funny, pics, article
overview:
Lolland is India’s biggest humour and comedy website.

Brought to you from the fictional republic of Lolland, you will tons of articles, jokes, pictures, videos and games that will have you laughing for hours. The site pokes fun at celebrities, cricket, politics, movies, news… pretty every thing you could think of. The forums have a great collection of funny pictures and pages found on the net.

Lolland also boasts of great participation from what they call the citizens of Lolland. Readers can give new article ideas as well as add their own thoughts to the current articles through comments, forum discussions or on their facebook page.

For a good time and lot of laughs, head over to Lolland.
